        <bioghist id="ref3">
            <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
            <p>Homer Hiram Lowry was a physical chemist at Bell Telephone Laboratories, inc. (1925-1930) and director of the Coal Research Laboratory at Carnegie Institute of Technology, Pittsburgh (1930-1953).</p>
